1
00:01:09,200 --> 00:01:10,330
Hahaha.

2
00:01:14,200 --> 00:01:15,450
Hahaha.

3
00:01:15,830 --> 00:01:17,870
The matter at the Liu residence was botched.

4
00:01:17,870 --> 00:01:21,470
Not a single weasel found out the true nature of the Soul Lantern.

5
00:01:22,039 --> 00:01:23,039
Spare me, My Lord.

6
00:01:23,200 --> 00:01:25,060
I already have a countermeasure.

7
00:01:25,750 --> 00:01:27,750
I will use the vengeful soul of Su Wanniang as bait

8
00:01:27,750 --> 00:01:29,150
to lure her into the trap.

9
00:01:30,830 --> 00:01:32,870
She will definitely be consumed by the resentment,

10
00:01:32,870 --> 00:01:33,870
deplete the spiritual power of the Soul Lantern,

11
00:01:33,870 --> 00:01:36,200
and disturb her and Xie Jingchen's peace.

12
00:01:36,370 --> 00:01:39,039
Su Wanniang is the daughter of the imperial censor

13
00:01:39,039 --> 00:01:40,830
who discovered our plot back then.

14
00:01:40,830 --> 00:01:41,830
Remember,

15
00:01:41,830 --> 00:01:43,789
your life is in my hands.

16
00:01:44,200 --> 00:01:46,000
If you mess up again this time,

17
00:01:46,160 --> 00:01:47,580
I wouldn't mind letting you

18
00:01:47,580 --> 00:01:49,910
end up like that old man from the Su family.

19
00:02:03,040 --> 00:02:05,450
General Xie, please save me,

20
00:02:06,000 --> 00:02:07,910
save my whole family.

21
00:02:09,539 --> 00:02:11,000
Vice Minister Zhou, speak plainly.

22
00:02:11,000 --> 00:02:13,160
Don't dirty my eyes with these gold and silver items.

23
00:02:13,160 --> 00:02:15,500
Something happened at the Yanyu Pavilion in the city.

24
00:02:15,500 --> 00:02:17,450
The pavilion's top courtesan, Su Wanniang,

25
00:02:17,450 --> 00:02:19,370
refused to submit to me a few days ago

26
00:02:19,370 --> 00:02:21,000
and burned herself to death in her room.

27
00:02:21,000 --> 00:02:22,160
But since then,

28
00:02:22,250 --> 00:02:23,700
any woman wearing red

29
00:02:23,700 --> 00:02:25,200
is haunted by resentment.

30
00:02:25,250 --> 00:02:26,310
If this continues,

31
00:02:26,329 --> 00:02:28,370
my whole family will die.

32
00:02:28,750 --> 00:02:30,620
You forced a civilian woman to death for your own selfish desires,

33
00:02:30,620 --> 00:02:32,620
and you dare to come asking for help?

34
00:02:32,620 --> 00:02:35,750
Men, arrest this scum who treats human life like dirt.

35
00:02:36,000 --> 00:02:36,829
Wait.

36
00:02:39,120 --> 00:02:40,450
Why are you stopping me?

37
00:02:41,160 --> 00:02:43,910
I'll go to the Yanyu Pavilion case.

38
00:02:45,000 --> 00:02:46,400
The Soul Lantern reacts.

39
00:02:46,660 --> 00:02:48,260
In Su Wanniang's obsession,

40
00:02:48,660 --> 00:02:51,260
there might be clues related to my background.

41
00:02:54,200 --> 00:02:56,400
If I find out you're lying even a little,

42
00:02:57,000 --> 00:02:59,410
I'll directly strip you of your official position

43
00:02:59,410 --> 00:03:00,910
and send you to the government office.

44
00:03:00,910 --> 00:03:01,660
Thank you,

45
00:03:01,660 --> 00:03:03,320
General, for sparing my life.

46
00:03:21,160 --> 00:03:23,000
General Xie, you're finally here.

47
00:03:23,000 --> 00:03:25,040
It's too weird in there.

48
00:03:25,160 --> 00:03:28,000
Several girls fainted right after entering that room on the second floor,

49
00:03:28,000 --> 00:03:29,660
and no one dares to go up again.

50
00:03:37,160 --> 00:03:38,290
Wait for me outside.

51
00:04:18,829 --> 00:04:20,490
Thank you for saving me, miss.

52
00:04:20,540 --> 00:04:22,330
May I ask who you are

53
00:04:22,330 --> 00:04:23,460
and why you are here?

54
00:04:23,540 --> 00:04:24,500
I am Qinghe

55
00:04:24,910 --> 00:04:26,080
from Yaowang Valley.

56
00:04:26,080 --> 00:04:28,540
I noticed a trace of resentment outside Yanyu Pavilion,

57
00:04:28,540 --> 00:04:30,940
so I was looking for the source in this room.

58
00:04:31,330 --> 00:04:33,370
I didn't expect someone to barge in.

59
00:04:36,700 --> 00:04:37,830
I am Adeng.

60
00:04:38,200 --> 00:04:40,330
Thank you for saving me just now.

61
00:04:41,000 --> 00:04:42,260
I'm also here for this.

62
00:04:48,409 --> 00:04:49,659
Ah.

63
00:04:49,830 --> 00:04:50,500
Help me.

64
00:05:00,870 --> 00:05:02,000
Ah.
